> Spec: [`spec.md`](./spec.md) • Context: [`context.md`](./context.md)
> Last updated: <YYYY-MM-DD>

The ADR-style log of architectural and design decisions for this work item. Each decision was
either **verified with the user** (when it shaped the spec or architecture) or **made by the
agent** (small implementation choices). Decisions verified with the user are marked.

**When a decision changes mid-workflow**: do **not** edit the original entry. Add a **new entry**
that supersedes it, mark the old one `superseded by D<N>`, and update the one-liner in `spec.md`.
Append a diary entry naming the change.

